ygData.messageBody:
I have also seen a lot of silly, funny and stupid names on my server.

Lets see:

Candy Cane

Allawannado Ishavsumfun

There are more but I cannot think of them (didnt write them down).

But we also have a paladin guildmate by the name of Arther Cloudchaser and,
we jokingly asked him if he was going to surname one of his alts (alts first
name is a variation on Arther) Fonzarelli.... Artherr Fonzarelli - I think
it's funny. I think if he does this I'm going to ask him where Ritchie
Cunningham is.... *grin*

======
Brangwen Incantare
28th Level Wood Elf Bard, The Rathe
======
